<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3150793" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1"><link href="text/schart/01/05020101.xhp" name="Alignment">Alignment</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3125864" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2">Modifies the alignment of the chart title.</paragraph>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3145748" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="4">Some of the options are not available for all types of labels. For example, there are different options for 2D and 3D object labels.</paragraph>
